{"tid":1099776,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駭入醫院LED屏發「日本萬歲」、「支持中國的是傻X」　IT男尋釁滋事遭刑事拘留","createTime":"2019-04-10T04:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T09:00:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff09204657d39760dc00429e7fe8847130e3aa5","tid":1099776,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T04:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190410/photo/bkn-20190410102617664-0410_00952_001_01p.jpg?20190410103802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190410%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190410102617664-0410_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20190410103802&h=aeed5760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190410/photo/bkn-20190410102617664-0410_00952_001_02b.jpg?20190410103802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190410%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190410102617664-0410_00952_001_02b.jpg%3F20190410103802&h=1a17abed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n河北保定市高陽縣一名31歲李姓男子，周一（8日）利用醫院一個LED屏幕發布辱華字句，引發關注，同日被當地警方逮捕。警方翌日再次發布通報，李男利用手機入侵醫院急症室網絡，控制LED屏幕，涉嫌尋釁滋事罪被刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n通報稱，李男當日陪同事到該醫院探病，期間利用手機連接該LED屏幕，發布言論。李男在當地一間通訊技術公司任職，因而有一定技術，懂得如何入侵醫院屏幕網絡。<br />\n<br />\n李男當天發布「日本萬歲」、「支持中國的是傻X」、「打到（倒）中國的帝國主義」等辱華字眼。事件發生後，醫院立即關閉LED屏幕電源並報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190410/bkn-20190410102617664-0410_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190410%2Fbkn-20190410102617664-0410_00952_001.html&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIgEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=13525a9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190410/bkn-20190410102617664-0410_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f7e164c71565e2ca3bea5a5549d04e519e1cce4d","tid":1099776,"uid":4661,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T04:09:41.000Z","msg":"期間利用手機連接該LED屏幕<br />\n<br />\nw